column5: Emergency foil hats on, everyone! We're about to hit the 75,000,000 views mark! Thanks  to all for helping our community grow and prosper.

got mine all ready to go !!!! this means the wearing of the extra special tinfoil hat !!!!
Thats impressive but all out of foil...used it for baked porkchops.  I'll have it ready for view #100,000,0000
You mean you guys take your foil hats off?? Crazy!!  S.

Hehehe!  Quite a testament this site... to how many people can talk about anything and everything... and a little fishing too. lol.  She's a big number Roy!  Holy Shmoley!
